Statebound built-in Rego rule library — synced into this directory at build
time from policies/builtin/*.rego. The Makefile target `authz-sync-bundle`
copies the rule files; the embed directive in ../embed.go picks them up via
//go:embed all:bundle/*.rego.

This file exists only so the empty bundle/ directory is committed to git and
the embed pattern compiles before the first sync runs. Do not write Rego
rules into this directory directly — author them in policies/builtin/ and
re-sync.
